OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith outbreaks of rain through Sunday
OL,7,Fand Monday with winds strengthening,
OL,8,Fbut still some good dry and bright or
OL,9,Fsunny spells. A mostly dry day Tuesday
OL,10,Fwith sunny spells.
